                        <p></p>
<p itemprop="description">
A poor village under attack by bandits recruits seven unemployed samurai to help them defend themselves.</p>
                        <p></p>
    <div class="txt-block" itemprop="director" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <h4 class="inline">Director:</h4>
<a href="/name/nm0000041/?ref_=tt_ov_dr" itemprop='url'><span class="itemprop" itemprop="name">Akira Kurosawa</span></a>
    </div>
    <div class="txt-block" itemprop="creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"> 
