        <h2>Storyline</h2>
        
        <div class="inline canwrap" itemprop="description">
            <p>
A veteran samurai, who has fallen on hard times, answers a village's request for protection from bandits. He gathers 6 other samurai to help him, and they teach the townspeople how to defend themselves, and they supply the samurai with three small meals a day. The film culminates in a giant battle when 40 bandits attack the village.                <em class="nobr">Written by
<a href="/search/title?plot_author=Colin Tinto <cst@imdb.com>&view=simple&sort=alpha&ref_=tt_stry_pl" >Colin Tinto &lt;cst@imdb.com&gt;</a></em>            </p>
        </div>
        
        <span class="see-more inline"> 
                <a href="/title/tt0047478/plotsummary?ref_=tt_stry_pl" >Plot Summary</a>
    <span>|</span>
        <a href="/title/tt0047478/synopsis?ref_=tt_stry_pl" >Plot Synopsis</a>
    </span>
        <hr />
